{"aid": "igkpl8sbbuu64z", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 4, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6rvi22aN6Q", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-04-18T08:33:35Z", "content": "<p>先前以为boot sector signature&#xff08;0x55aa&#xff09;验证在bootloader中做。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>可在做lab1练习2时&#xff0c;没有发现bootloader检查引导扇区的这个签名&#xff0c;只看到由bootloader装入8个磁盘扇区后核对kernel映像是否符合ELF格式。&#xff08;好像boot时&#xff0c;ucore没有分MBR和活动分区&#xff0c;直接在一个扇区代码中加载kernel&#xff08;映像&#xff09;&#xff08;即所谓Single Stage Bootloader&#xff09;&#xff0c;对此我没有仔细分析。&#xff09;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>qemu绑定的BIOS是开源的SeaBIOS&#xff0c;查看其boot.c源文件中有MBR_SIGNATURE&#xff08;0xaa55&#xff09;判断----原来由BIOS来检查这个签名。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>仔细一想&#xff0c;BIOS加载磁盘扇区到RAM&#xff0c;如果由bootloader来验证boot sector签名&#xff0c;因为这个签名又是扇区为bootloader的保障&#xff0c;就会陷入先有鸡还是先有蛋的矛盾境地。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>为避免发生程序控制权进入一个无效的bootloader情况&#xff08;可能导致意想不到的后果&#xff09;&#xff0c;由BIOS验证boot sector signature来得安全可靠&#xff08;如果签名不对&#xff0c;可由BIOS显示&#34;Boot failed: not a bootable disk&#34;&#xff0c;然后死机&#xff09;。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>我的想法全面吗&#xff1f;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>&#xff08;顺便提一下&#xff0c;在实验楼目前可以做实验到lab2&#xff0c;请课程组开启剩余的实验项目。&#xff09;</p>", "subject": "原来boot sector signature验证是在BIOS中执行"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": ["hdjonbiyfs62ie"], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446635776186, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-04-18T09:18:52Z", "id": "i8mtbw8tfnq3d0", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-04-18T09:18:52Z", "content": "<p>你关于数字签名的验证方的描述是准确的。分析得很好。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>需要说明的是&#xff0c;这个数字签名仅能验证这个引导扇区是一个符合格式要求的引导扇区&#xff0c;并没有安全可靠方面的保证。</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "i6rvi22aN6Q", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-04-18T12:40:50Z", "id": "i8n0jmzfer25f8", "updated": "2015-04-18T12:40:50Z", "subject": "<p>明白了&#xff0c;“签名正确”不是“有效的bootloader”的充分条件&#xff0c;在SeaBIOS中是当作必要条件&#xff0c;只能讲一个签名正确的引导扇区是符合格式要求的。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>或许说“引导扇区签名的验证方是BIOS比是bootloader要合理”准确。</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 3, "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_upvotes": 0, "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "children": [{"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2015-04-18T15:29:32Z", "id": "i8n6kkrosig7p7", "updated": "2015-04-18T15:29:32Z", "subject": "<p>理解准确。</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 3, "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "children": [], "type": "feedback"}], "type": "followup"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-04-19T07:59:23Z", "id": "i8o5xj94hgd5jr", "updated": "2015-04-19T07:59:23Z", "subject": "<p>在实验楼注册后&#xff0c;可以一个实验一个实验地做&#xff0c;所有实验都打开了。不过只有选择了前一个实验后&#xff0c;在文档最后点击“下一个实验”&#xff0c;才能到下一个实验。</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [], "type": "followup"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 50, "created": "2015-04-18T08:33:35Z", "id": "i8mrpo96ybt4kh", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 312, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["lab1"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6rvi22aN6Q", "when": "2015-04-18T08:33:35Z", "data": "i8mrpo98uoi4ki", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "when": "2015-04-18T09:18:52Z", "data": "i8mtbw8yd9v3d1", "to": "i8mrpo96ybt4kh", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "i6rvi22aN6Q", "when": "2015-04-18T12:40:50Z", "to": "i8mrpo96ybt4kh", "anon": "no", "type": "followup"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "when": "2015-04-18T15:29:32Z", "to": "i8mrpo96ybt4kh", "anon": "no", "type": "feedback"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "when": "2015-04-19T07:59:23Z", "to": "i8mrpo96ybt4kh", "anon": "no", "type": "followup"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "tag_good": [{"class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "name": "Yong XIANG", "id": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "photo": null, "admin": true, "us": false}]}}